OL,3,CTrump threatens 'big tariff' on UK
OL,4,Cover digital tax on US tech firms
OL,6,FUS President Donald Trump has
OL,7,Fthreatened to impose tariffs on the UK
OL,8,Fif it does not drop its digital
OL,9,Fservices tax on American social media
OL,10,Ffirms.
OL,12,FThe digital services tax, introduced
OL,13,Fin 2020, imposes a 2% levy on the
OL,14,Frevenues of several major US tech
OL,15,Fcompanies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
