PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776999825
OL,3,CTrump threatens 'big tariff' on UK
OL,4,Cover digital tax on US tech firms
OL,6,FSpeaking to reporters from the Oval
OL,7,FOffice on Thursday, Mr Trump said:
OL,8,F"We've been looking at it and we can
OL,9,Fmeet that very easily by just putting
OL,10,Fa big tariff on the UK, so they better
OL,11,Fbe careful.
OL,13,F"If they don't drop the tax, we'll
OL,14,Fprobably put a big tariff on the UK."
OL,16,FThe tax targets companies whose
OL,17,Fworldwide revenues from digital
OL,18,Factivities exceed #500 million, with
OL,19,Fmore than #25 million of the revenues
OL,20,Ffrom UK users.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOUvD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776999825
OL,3,CTrump threatens 'big tariff' on UK
OL,4,Cover digital tax on US tech firms
OL,6,FMr Trump argued the laws, which have
OL,7,Flong been a source of tension in UK-US
OL,8,Frelations, targeted "top companies in
OL,9,Fthe world".
OL,11,F"The UK did it, a couple of other
OL,12,Fpeople did it," he said.
OL,14,F"They think they're going to make an
OL,15,Feasy buck, that's why they've all
OL,16,Ftaken advantage of our country."
OL,18,FThe digital services tax went
OL,19,Funchanged under the UK`US trade deal
OL,20,Fagreed in May 2025, despite being a
OL,21,Fpoint of discussion.
OL,26,@pD@UOUqD@JO]sD@AOUtD@OO]vD@AOUxD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776999825
OL,3,CTrump threatens 'big tariff' on UK
OL,4,Cover digital tax on US tech firms
OL,6,FAsked how high the tariff would be,
OL,7,Fthe president said it would be "more
OL,8,Fthan what they're getting" from the
OL,9,Flevy.
OL,11,F"What we'll do is we'll reciprocate by
OL,12,Fputting something on that's equal or
OL,13,Fgreater than what they're doing," he
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,FThe latest remarks add to wider
OL,17,Fstrains in UK-US relations, which have
OL,18,Fdeteriorated after Sir Keir Starmer
OL,19,Fruled out British involvement in the
OL,20,Fconflict in the Middle East.
OL,26,@oD@`OUpD@ZO]sD@AOUuD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
