PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776999825
OL,3,CTrump threatens 'big tariff' on UK
OL,4,Cover digital tax on US tech firms
OL,6,FEarlier this month, Mr Trump suggested
OL,7,Fthe terms of the UK-US trade agreement
OL,8,Fbrokered last year "can always be
OL,9,Fchanged" in an interview with Sky News.
OL,11,FSpeaking at Prime Minister's Questions
OL,12,Fin the House of Commons, Sir Keir
OL,13,Faddressed pressure from the US over
OL,14,Fthe Iran war.
OL,16,FHe told MPs: "My position on the Iran
OL,17,Fwar has been clear from the start.
OL,18,FWe're not going to get dragged into
OL,19,Fthis war. It is not our war.
OL,26,@pD@TOUqD@HO]xD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776999825
OL,3,CTrump threatens 'big tariff' on UK
OL,4,Cover digital tax on US tech firms
OL,6,F"A lot of pressure has been applied to
OL,7,Fme to take a different course, and
OL,8,Fthat pressure included what happened
OL,9,Flast night.
OL,11,F"I'm not going to change my mind. I'm
OL,12,Fnot going to yield.
OL,14,F"It is not in our national interest to
OL,15,Fjoin this war, and we will not do so.
OL,16,FI know where I stand."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@AOUxD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
