OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776999825
OL,3,CTrump threatens 'big tariff' on UK
OL,4,Cover digital tax on US tech firms
OL,6,FMr Trump's comments come months after
OL,7,Fsimilar US threats to impose new
OL,8,Ftariffs and export controls on
OL,9,Fcountries with digital taxes or
OL,10,Fregulations affecting American tech
OL,11,Fgiants.
OL,13,FA number of European countries, like
OL,14,FFrance, Italy and Spain, have a
OL,15,Fdigital services tax.
OL,17,FIn a post on Truth Social from August
OL,18,F2025, Mr Trump said he would "stand up
OL,19,Fto countries that attack our
OL,20,Fincredible American Tech Companies".
OL,26,@zD@^OU|D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
