PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1776999825
OL,3,CTrump threatens 'big tariff' on UK
OL,4,Cover digital tax on US tech firms
OL,6,F"Digital Taxes, Digital Services
OL,7,FLegislation, and Digital Markets
OL,8,FRegulations are all designed to harm,
OL,9,For discriminate against, American
OL,10,FTechnology," he wrote.
OL,12,F"This must end," he said and vowed
OL,13,Fthat "unless these discriminatory
OL,14,Factions are removed", he would "impose
OL,15,Fsubstantial additional tariffs" on the
OL,16,Foffending nation's exports to the US.
OL,18,FDowning Street has been contacted for
OL,19,Fcomment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@LO]tD@AOUtD@PO]uD@FOUvD@TO]vD@
